1 Month Ago During the attack, three policemen were killed while the station and two vehicles were burnt. The latest development comes a few days after about three persons were confirmed dead and many others injured in an explosion that occurred in Kabba. Saharareporters had reported how military intelligence showed that ISWAP is moving towards the Southern part of Nigeria.  